name: Red Fox Blessed Father Saint Amalgamate
description: Not a single fox image was used to create this; in a remarkable artifact of AI consciousness, in the very first run through of generative machine dreaming being fed a photo of the 2nd saint statue that was manually edited and prepped to be sent through the AI, we were blessed with an uncanny red fox Soul trapping himself in the image and haunting it. All the other runs back and forth for hours between generative AI, manual detailing and personalization, human and mechanical image blending and mutating = we arrive at this cozy digital home for this little red fox Soul: the 2nd release in the "Saint Amalgamations" collection.
